	"description": "Sounds pretty hard, right?\n\nCreating a traditional business is a great struggle. Finding clients, polishing\nyour product, making payroll, finding the right employees, automating\nprocesses…Since there are so many moving parts, you’re always wondering — Where\ndo I focus now? Am I doing the right things? What should I be doing next?\n\nAnd if you are trying to build a social or an open-source business or a\ncooperative, there are even more moving parts.\n\nBuilding a business\nA traditional entrepreneur ",
